 Csongr\u00e1d County\n| align=\"right\"| '''4,262.71'''\n|align=\"right\"| '''417,456'''\n| align=\"right\"| '''98'''\n|'''[[Szeged]]'''\n| align=\"center\"|'''60'''\n|}\n\n== Transport ==\n\n=== Road network ===\n[[File:E75 Roszke.JPG|thumbnail|right|M5 motorway near R\u00f6szke.]]\n[[File:Szentes Attila \u00fat ker\u00e9kp\u00e1r\u00fat 2012-12-31.JPG|thumbnail|right|Main road 45 near Szentes.]]\n{{see also|Roads in Hungary|Highways in Hungary}}\nIn 2012, Csongr\u00e1d County has a dense network of public roads, in total length of 1,350&nbsp;km, of which 281&nbsp;km are main roads.<ref name=\"monografie\">{{cite journal |url=http://m.delmagyar.hu/delm/k02_munkaanyag.pdf |title=Csongr\u00e1d Megyei Ter\u00fclet fejleszt\u00e9si Koncepci\u00f3 |pages= |language=Hungarian}}</ref> Inland, connections are provided by 1,049&nbsp;km of county and communal roads and 20&nbsp;km are covered with light road surfaces.\n\n;Highway network\n*[[File:M5 (Hu) Otszogletu kek tabla.svg|30px|link=M5 motorway (Hungary)]] [[File:E75-HUN.svg|30px|link=European route E75]] runs from [[Budapest]] to [[R\u00f6szke]] ([[Serbia]]n border). ~ 47&nbsp;km \n*[[File:M9 (Hu) Otszogletu kek tabla.svg|30px|link=M9 expressway (Hungary)]] ''runs from [[Szombathely]] to [[Szeged]]. (planned)''\n*[[File:M43 (Hu) Otszogletu kek tabla.svg|30px|link=M43 motorway (Hungary)]] [[File:E68-HUN.svg|30px|link=European route E68]] runs from Szeged to [[Csan\u00e1dpalota]] ([[Romania]]n border). - 58&nbsp;km\n\n;Road network\n*[[File:5 (Hu) Otszogletu zold tabla.svg|25px]] runs from Budapest to R\u00f6szke (Serbian border), via [[Kistelek]] and Szeged. - 52&nbsp;km\n*[[File:43 (Hu) Otszogletu zold tabla.svg|25px]] runs from Szeged to [[Nagylak]], via [[Mak\u00f3]]. - 55&nbsp;km\n*430 runs from Mak\u00f3 to [[H\u00f3dmez\u0151v\u00e1s\u00e1rhely]]. - 30&nbsp;km\n*[[File:431 (Hu) Otszogletu zold tabla.svg|25px]] runs from Mak\u00f3 to [[Kiszombor]] (Romanian border). - 6&nbsp;km\n*[[File:45 (Hu) Otszogletu zold tabla.svg|25px]] runs from [[Kunszentm\u00e1rton]] to H\u00f3dmez\u0151v\u00e1s\u00e1rhely, via [[Szentes]]. - 43&nbsp;km\n*[[File:47 (Hu) Otszogletu zold tabla.svg|25px]] runs from Szeged to [[Debrecen]], via H\u00f3dmez\u0151v\u00e1s\u00e1rhely.\n*[[File:55 (Hu) Otszogletu zold tabla.svg|25px]] runs from Szeged to [[B\u00e1tasz\u00e9k]], via [[M\u00f3rahalom]].\n*[[File:451 (Hu) Otszogletu zold tabla.svg|25px]] runs from [[Kiskunf\u00e9legyh\u00e1za]] to Szentes, via [[Csongr\u00e1d]].\n*[[File:502 (Hu) Otszogletu zold tabla.svg|25px]] ''western bypass of Szeged.''\n\n== Politics ==\n{{Main article|Csongr\u00e1d County Assembly}}\nThe Csongr\u00e1d County Council, elected at the [[2019 Hungarian local elections|2019 local government elections]], is made up of 20 counselors<ref>{{cite web|title=Megyei k\u00f6zgy\u0171l\u00e9s tagjai 2019-2024 (Csongr\u00e1d megye)|url=https://www.valasztas.hu/megye-adatlap_onk2019?_onknavigacio_WAR_nvinvrportlet_formDate=32503680000000&p_p_id=onknavigacio_WAR_nvinvrportlet&p_p_lifecycle=1&p_p_state=normal&p_p_mode=view&p_p_col_id=column-2&p_p_col_pos=1&p_p_col_count=3&_onknavigacio_WAR_nvinvrportlet_prpVlId=294&_onknavigacio_WAR_nvinvrportlet_prpVltId=687&_onknavigacio_WAR_nvinvrportlet_prpMegyeKod=06&_onknavigacio_WAR_nvinvrportlet_prpTelepulesKod=&_onknavigacio_WAR_nvinvrportlet_settlement=csongr%C3%A1d|agency=valasztas.hu|accessdate=2019-10-29}}</ref>, with the following party composition:\n\n{| cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"1\" class=\"wikitable\"\n! style=\"background:#ccc\" colspan=\"2\" | Party\n! style=\"background:#ccc\" | Seats\n! style=\"background:#ccc\" colspan=\"12\" | Current County Assembly\n|-\n| style=\"background-color: {{Fidesz/meta/color}}  | &nbsp;\n|[[Fidesz]]-[[Christian Democratic People's Party (Hungary)|KDNP]]\n| style=\"text-align: right\" | '''12'''\n|style=\"background-color: {{Fidesz/meta/color}} | &nbsp;\n|style=\"background-color: {{Fidesz/meta/color}} | &nbsp;\n|style=\"background-color