e=\"background-color: #8E6FCE  | &nbsp;\n| [[Momentum Movement]]\n| style=\"text-align: right\" | '''1'''\n|style=\"background-color: #8E6FCE | &nbsp;\n| &nbsp;\n| &nbsp;\n| &nbsp;\n| &nbsp;\n| &nbsp;\n| &nbsp;\n| &nbsp;\n| &nbsp;\n| &nbsp;\n| &nbsp;\n| &nbsp;\n|}\n\n===Presidents of the General Assembly===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"  style=\"float:left; margin-left:1em;\"\n|- \"\n! colspan=\"2\"|List of Presidents, from 1990<ref>[http://valtor.valasztas.hu/valtort/jsp/t0.jsp \u00d6nkorm\u00e1nyzati v\u00e1laszt\u00e1sok eredm\u00e9nyei] {{in lang|hu}}</ref>\n|---- bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\"\n|[[Istv\u00e1n Lehmann]] ([[Hungarian Socialist Party|MSZP]])||1990\u20131998\n|---- bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\"\n|[[J\u00f3zsef Frank (politician)|Dr. J\u00f3zsef Frank]] ([[Fidesz]])||1998\u20132006\n|---- bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\"\n|[[Anna Magyar]] (Fidesz-[[Christian Democratic People's Party (Hungary)|KDNP]])||2006\u20132014\n|---- bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\"\n|[[B\u00e9la Kakas]] (Fidesz-KDNP)||2014\u2013\n|}\n{{clear}}\n\n== Municipalities ==\nCsongr\u00e1d County has '''2''' [[Town with county rights|urban counties]], '''8''' [[List of cities and towns of Hungary|towns]], '''7''' large villages and '''43''' villages.\n\nAs a typical Great Plain county, Csongr\u00e1d has a relatively small number of municipalities. 72.5% of the population lives in cities/towns, so it is one of the most urbanized county in Hungary.<ref>[http://www.nepszamlalas.hu/eng/volumes/06/06/tabeng/4/load01_1_0.html List of localities in Csongr\u00e1d county by area, population and status (2001 census), English]</ref>\n\n;Cities with county rights\n(ordered by population, as of 2011 [[census]])\n*[[Szeged]] (168,048) \u2013 county seat\n*[[H\u00f3dmez\u0151v\u00e1s\u00e1rhely]] (46,047)\n\n;Towns\n{{Div col|colwidth=25em}}\n*[[Szentes]] (28,509)\n*[[Mak\u00f3]] (23,683)\n*[[Csongr\u00e1d]] (17,242)\n*[[S\u00e1ndorfalva]] (7,871)\n*[[Kistelek]] (7,103)\n*[[Mindszent]] (6,914)\n*[[M\u00f3rahalom]] (5,804)\n*[[Csan\u00e1dpalota]] (2,923)\n{{Div col end}}\n\n;Villages\n{{Div col|colwidth=15em}}\n*[[Algy\u0151]] [[File:Red pog.svg|8px]]\n*[[Ambr\u00f3zfalva]]\n*[[Ap\u00e1tfalva]]\n*[[\u00c1rp\u00e1dhalom]]\n*[[\u00c1sotthalom]] [[File:Red pog.svg|8px]]\n*[[Baks]]\n*[[Bal\u00e1stya]]\n*[[Bord\u00e1ny]]\n*[[Csan\u00e1dalberti]]\n*[[Csanytelek]]\n*[[Csengele]]\n*[[Derekegyh\u00e1z]]\n*[[Deszk]]\n*[[Domasz\u00e9k]]\n*[[D\u00f3c]]\n*[[Eperjes]]\n*[[F\u00e1bi\u00e1nsebesty\u00e9n]]\n*[[Felgy\u0151]]\n*[[Ferencsz\u00e1ll\u00e1s]]\n*[[Forr\u00e1sk\u00fat]]\n*[[F\u00f6lde\u00e1k]]\n*[[Kir\u00e1lyhegyes]]\n*[[Kiszombor]] [[File:Red pog.svg|8px]]\n*[[Kl\u00e1rafalva]]\n*[[K\u00f6vegy]]\n*[[K\u00fcbekh\u00e1za]]\n*[[Magyarcsan\u00e1d]]\n*[[Maroslele]]\n*[[M\u00e1rt\u00e9ly]]\n*[[Nagy\u00e9r]]\n*[[Nagylak]]\n*[[Nagym\u00e1gocs]] [[File:Red pog.svg|8px]]\n*[[Nagyt\u0151ke]]\n*[[\u00d3f\u00f6lde\u00e1k]]\n*[[\u00d3pusztaszer]] [[File:Red pog.svg|8px]]\n*[[\u00d6tt\u00f6m\u00f6s]]\n*[[Pitvaros]]\n*[[Pusztam\u00e9rges]]\n*[[Pusztaszer]]\n*[[R\u00f6szke]]\n*[[Ruzsa]]\n*[[Szatymaz]]\n*[[Szegv\u00e1r]] [[File:Red pog.svg|8px]]\n*[[Sz\u00e9kkutas]]\n*[[Tiszasziget]]\n*[[T\u00f6m\u00f6rk\u00e9ny]]\n*[[\u00dajszentiv\u00e1n]]\n*[[\u00dcll\u00e9s]]\n*[[Z\u00e1k\u00e1nysz\u00e9k]]\n*[[Zsomb\u00f3]]\n{{Div col end}}\n[[File:Red pog.svg|8px]] municipalities are ''large'' villages.\n\n== Gallery ==\n<center>\n<gallery widths=\"200\" heights=\"200px\" perrow=\"6\" style=\"border: 5px solid #a86; box-shadow: 0.1em 0.1em 0.5em rgba(0,0,0,0.75); border-radius: 0.5em;\">\nFile:Fogadalmi templom (12498. sz\u00e1m\u00fa m\u0171eml\u00e9k) 19.jpg|[[Szeged]], the capital of the county\nFile:Megyeh\u00e1za (3538. sz\u00e1m\u00fa m\u0171eml\u00e9k) 45.jpg|County hall in [[Szentes]]\nFile:T\u00e1p\u00e9-R\u00e9t.JPG|[[Great Hungarian Plain]] in Csongr\u00e1d County\nFile:Sz\u00e9lmalom (3523. sz\u00e1m\u00fa m\u0171eml\u00e9k) 3.jpg|Windmill near Szeged\nFile:Volt K\u00e1rolyi-kast\u00e9ly (3426. sz\u00e1m\u00fa m\u0171eml\u00e9k) 2.jp